      @{"Show Stats     " link "Show Stats"}
      @{"Quit           " link "Quit"}

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Undo Last"
@{b}Undo Last@{ub}

Will undo the last move made.

You can undo the last 30 moves.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "New Game"
@{b}New Game@{ub}

Will start a new game with a freshly sorted stack of cards.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Same Game"
@{b}Same Game@{ub}

Will restart the game you are currently playing.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Easy Normal Game"
@{b}Easy Game/Normal Game@{ub}

The easy game is the same as the normal game but without the full set
of cards.

You cannot really lose with this game and so is useful for learning
the rules or for children to play.

Playing the easy game will not affect the game statistics.

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Show Stats"
@{b}Show Stats@{ub}

Displays a window of interesting statistics on your game play.

If more than one person plays on the same Amiga make multiple
copies of the program in different draws and compare performance !


@ENDNODE

@NODE "Quit"
@{b}Quit@{ub}

Will exit from the program.
@ENDNODE



